components.kdoc:
Aurum's icon-only button primitive.

Wraps `material3.IconButton` internally, preserving its 48 dp minimum
touch target. Features consume this composable — never
`material3.IconButton` directly.

The [content] slot typically renders an [AurumIcon]. The caller controls
the icon size and tint via [AurumIcon]'s parameters.

@param onClick called when the button is clicked
@param modifier the [Modifier] to apply
@param enabled whether the button is interactive — defaults to `true`
@param content the composable content — typically an [AurumIcon]

