components.kdoc:
A status-tinted transaction row for payment / withdrawal / savings history lists.
Outer `feedback.*` wash wraps a white inner card with leading icon, label + date,
status badge, and amount (+ optional gold-weight suffix). [helperText] renders below
in the matching status colour.

@param label transaction label; ellipsises past one line
@param dateText pre-formatted date (e.g. `"18 Sep • 7:00 pm"`)
@param amount pre-formatted amount (e.g. `"₹ 100"`)
@param suffixText optional gold-weight suffix (e.g. `"0.0045 gms"`); `null` to hide
@param status validation state — drives wash, badge icon, and amount/helper colour
@param modifier the [Modifier] to apply
@param helperText explanatory text below the inner card in the status colour; `null` to hide
@param leading optional 40 dp slot for the row's leading visual — caller provides
  any composable (AurumIcon at its natural size, remote-image loader, Lottie, etc.).
  Aurum reserves a centred 40 dp box; the slot's content is centred inside.

