Aurum's canonical text primitive.

Wraps [BasicText] (not `material3.Text`) and applies Aurum typography
tokens. If no [style] is provided, defaults to [Aurum.type.bodyMRegular].

### Foreground resolution order
1. Explicit [color] parameter — overrides anything in [style], including a [Brush].
2. `style.brush` — gradient text passes through untouched (use `Aurum.type.foo.copy(brush = myBrush)`
   or construct a `TextStyle(brush = …, …)`).
3. `style.color` — honoured if set.
4. Aurum's default text colour ([Aurum.colors.surface.textDefaultNormal]).

This is a **scratch** component — built on `androidx.compose.foundation`
with zero `material3` imports.

